{
  "total_duration": 489.58,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 13.14,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "如果学校走廊里贴着“严禁奔跑，违者处罚”，你可能会立刻紧张。可如果另一张提醒写着：“欢迎来到这里，请慢慢走，注意安全，这只是一个提醒。”你是不是更愿意照做？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 13.49,
      "end": 27.53,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "A polite request"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“彬彬有礼的要求”。这篇课文不是让小朋友学习停车规则，而是看同一个规则，怎样用更礼貌、更清楚的语气说出来。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 27.88,
      "end": 45.04,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先把旧场景接到现在。课文里是车停错了地方；你可以换成共享单车停错区、图书馆里需要安静、走廊里不要奔跑、博物馆里不要触摸展品。核心都是：有规则，也有人提醒你遵守规则。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 45.389,
      "end": 59.957,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "traffic policeman"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是管理道路交通和停车规则的交通警察。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "No Parking"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "area 是禁止停车区域。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "street signs"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是街道上的规则标志。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 60.307,
      "end": 74.651,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "还有一个很重要的词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "ticket"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这里不是电影票，也不是火车票，而是 parking ticket，停车罚单。作者本来以为自己会收到罚单，结果看到的是一张非常礼貌的 note。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 75.001,
      "end": 84.841,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Sweden 瑞典只是故事发生的度假地点。我们不用把它讲成文化课，只要知道：作者在那里收到了一张城市写给游客的礼貌提醒。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 85.19,
      "end": 96.782,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "记住，polite 不是模糊不清。那张 note 很客气，但规则很明确："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "This is a \"No Parking\" area."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "礼貌和清楚，可以同时存在。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 97.132,
      "end": 112.952,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一帧，作者把车停在了不该停车的地方。课文开头直接给了规则和结果："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "If you park your car in the wrong place, a traffic policeman will soon find it."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "如果停车地点不对，交通警察很快会发现。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 113.302,
      "end": 130.574,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二帧，作者知道接下来可能会发生什么："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "You will be very lucky if he lets you go without a ticket."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "如果警察没有给你罚单就放你走，你就很幸运。这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "without a ticket"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“没有罚单”，不是“没有车票”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 130.923,
      "end": 147.763,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三帧，故事转向了。作者在瑞典度假时，在车上发现了一张 note。它不是冷冰冰的处罚通知，而是先说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sir, we welcome you to our city."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先欢迎，再提醒，语气立刻不一样。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 148.113,
      "end": 164.097,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四帧，note 继续说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "This is a \"No Parking\" area."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "规则很清楚。然后它又说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "You will enjoy your stay here if you pay attention to our street signs."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后补一句："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "This note is only a reminder."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 164.447,
      "end": 174.278,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以作者最后说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "If you receive a request like this, you cannot fail to obey it!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这样一张既礼貌又清楚的提醒，让人很难不照做。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 174.628,
      "end": 179.428,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这篇课文有趣的地方，不是“停车”本身，而是语气的力量。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 179.778,
      "end": 182.72,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么作者本来会想到 ticket？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 183.07,
      "end": 192.954,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为他停错地方了。通常你会想到冷冰冰的罚单，或者很严厉的命令。所以"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "ticket"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里就是停车罚单。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 193.304,
      "end": 196.126,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那这张 note 为什么有效？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 196.476,
      "end": 209.172,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "它先欢迎作者："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "we welcome you to our city"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这让人感觉自己是被尊重的客人。可是它没有把规则藏起来，它直接说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "This is a \"No Parking\" area."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 209.522,
      "end": 211.912,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以 polite 不是绕来绕去？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 212.262,
      "end": 221.502,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。真正好的 polite request 是先尊重对方，再把规则说清楚。它不是吓唬你，而是帮助你注意到规则。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 221.851,
      "end": 226.116,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "cannot fail to obey it"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "听起来有点绕。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 226.466,
      "end": 235.946,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以简单理解成：你一定会遵守它，你很难不照做。因为这张 request 既有礼貌，又有理由，又很清楚。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
