    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 339.527,
      "end": 349.862,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的 grammar 是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "if... will..."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，也就是“如果怎样，就会怎样”。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "if"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "给条件，另一半告诉你结果。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 350.212,
      "end": 363.292,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先看第一句："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "If you park your car in the wrong place, a traffic policeman will soon find it."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "条件是 you park in the wrong place，结果是 a traffic policeman will find it。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 363.642,
      "end": 375.802,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这个顺序也可以反过来："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "You will be very lucky if he lets you go without a ticket."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先说结果 you will be very lucky，再说条件 if he lets you go without a ticket。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 376.152,
      "end": 387.087,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "note 里也用了同样的链条："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "You will enjoy your stay here if you pay attention to our street signs."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "如果你注意街道标志，你在这里会过得更愉快。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 387.437,
      "end": 400.913,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课只需要记住实用结构："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "if"
