          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Welcome to our library. This is a quiet area. You will enjoy your reading if you pay attention to the signs. This note is only a reminder."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以写走廊、图书馆、共享单车停车区，也可以写教室规则。"
